package it.polimi.ingsw.am37.message
  • Class
    Description
    ActiveLobbiesMessage
    This message is provided to advertise all open lobby to the client when tries to connect.
    ChooseCloudMessage
    This message is used at the end of turn to select from which clouds get the students to insert into the new entranceRoom
    ChooseTeamMessage
    This message is used to select a desired wizardTeam in a lobby before the starting of a match.
    ConfirmMessage
    General confirm message.
    EndGameMessage
    Message sent at the end of a match
    ErrorMessage
    This message is used to comunicate that an error occur when last request have been performed.
    LobbyRequestMessage
    This message is used to request to join a lobby providing desired settings, such as advanced rules enabled or the number of players.
    LoginMessage
    This is a message sent by the client when try to log in to the server.
    Message
    Abstract class for representing the message and its basic functionality.
    MessageGsonBuilder
    Personalized builder of google Gson object to enable the polymorphic serialization and deserialization of messages.
    MessageJSONTests
    Class used for testing gson
    MessageType
    Enumeration of possible messages between server and clients
    MoveMotherNatureMessage
    This message is used to communicate the mother nature destination as regular movements; for movements associated to special characters please use PlayCharacterMessage.
    NextTurnMessage
    This message is sent by server when a new player have to play.
    PingMessage
    Simple message to check the connection
    PlanningPhaseMessage
    This message is sent by server when a new player have to play.
    PlayAssistantMessage
    This message is used to represent the intents to play an assistant.
    PlayCharacterMessage
    This message is used to comunicate the intent to play a character.
    ResilienceMessage
    Message used for notifying disconnection or re-connection
    RuntimeTypeAdapterFactory<T>
    Personal extensions and implementation of this
    StartGameMessage
    This message is sent by the lobby when is ready to accept players moves.
    StudentsToDiningMessage
    This message is used to move students from entrance to the dining room of a player.
    StudentsToIslandMessage
    This message is used to move students from entrance to an Island.
    UpdateMessage
    This message is used to share relevant information about the updated objects after each action.
